          I am a Frontend Web Developer specializing in crafting scalable and
          high-performance web applications. I am passionate about delivering
          exceptional user experiences through thoughtful design and optimized
          front-end solutions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-[150px_1fr]'>
        <p class='text-sm md:text-base'><b>Education</b></p>
        <p class='opacity-60 text-sm md:text-base'>
          I graduated with a degree in Systems Engineering and Computation from
          Universidad Tecnol√≥gica de Pereira in 2022.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-[150px_1fr]'>
        <p class='text-sm md:text-base'><b>Experience</b></p>
        <p class='opacity-60 text-sm md:text-base'>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Voluptate
